data.description: You have to see this modern masterpiece, in the very desirable Port Charlotte area. The home features two bedrooms and two bathrooms and has been fully remodeled. The water heater was replaced in 2014, the roof in 2016, the HVAC in 2017, all impact resistant windows and doors in 2019. The property was recently painted, has new waterproof 50 year warranty luxury vinyl plank flooring, new granite, new stainless steel appliances, new shaker cabinets etc. No detail was left untouched. Be sure to schedule a showing, you will not be disappointed.
